(1, 'Version 8 of Angular — Smaller bundles, CLI APIs, and alignment with the ecosystem', '<p id=\"46b2\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">The 8.0.0 release of Angular is here! This is a major release spanning the entire platform, including the framework, Angular Material, and the CLI with synchronized major versions. This release improves application startup time on modern browsers, provides new APIs for tapping into the CLI, and aligns Angular to the ecosystem and more web standards.</p><figure class=\"ls lt lu lv lw fg y z paragraph-image\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 56px auto 0px; clear: both; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"lx ly eu lz ac\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; width: 680px; position: relative; transition: transform 300ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0.2, 1) 0s; cursor: zoom-in; z-index: auto;\"><div class=\"y z lr\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1390px;\"><div class=\"md l eu me\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; margin: auto; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\"><div class=\"mf l\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding-bottom: 373.266px;\"><div class=\"dn ma gt n o gs ac cp mb mc\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 680px; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0; height: 373.266px; position: absolute; transition: opacity 100ms ease 400ms; will-change: transform; transform: translateZ(0px);\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"gt n o gs ac mg mh ob oc\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/30/1*RAjXU6nFJ_LbUS5nH3acsQ.jpeg?q=20\" width=\"1390\" height=\"763\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 680px; height: 373.266px; position: absolute; filter: blur(20px); transform: scale(1.1); visibility: hidden; transition: visibility 0ms ease 400ms;\"></div><img alt=\"\" class=\"nu nv gt n o gs ac gq\" width=\"1390\" height=\"763\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1390/1*RAjXU6nFJ_LbUS5nH3acsQ.jpeg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 680px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 373.266px; position: absolute; opacity: 1; transition: opacity 400ms ease 0ms;\"></div></div></div></div><figcaption class=\"cf ej mj mk hv dl y z ml mm aw ei\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.54); max-width: 728px; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; margin-top: 10px;\">Photo by Angular TPM, Manu Murthy</figcaption></figure><h1 id=\"472c\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\">How to update to version 8</h1><p id=\"862d\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Visit&nbsp;<a href=\"https://update.angular.io/\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">update.angular.io</a>&nbsp;for detailed information and guidance. For most developers, one command should take care of this update:</p><p id=\"247f\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng update @angular/cli @angular/core</code></p><h1 id=\"14b3\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\"><span class=\"bj\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Differential Loading by Default</span></h1><p id=\"0ef8\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><a href=\"https://web.dev/codelab-serve-modern-code\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Differential loading</a>&nbsp;is a process by which the browser chooses between modern or legacy JavaScript based on its own capabilities. We now take advantage of this by default by performing a modern build (es2015) and a legacy build (es5) of your application. When users load your application, they’ll automatically get the bundle they need.</p><p id=\"977a\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">If you use&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng update,</code>&nbsp;we update your&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">tsconfig.json</code>for you to take advantage of this. Our CLI looks at the&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">target</code>&nbsp;JS level in your&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">tsconfig.json</code>&nbsp;to determine whether or not to take advantage of Differential Loading.</p><figure class=\"ls lt lu lv lw fg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"md l eu\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; margin: auto;\"><div class=\"rl l\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding-bottom: 236.984px;\"><iframe src=\"https://blog.angular.io/media/29f823745a5a9feaedc4e4734735dc39\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"237\" width=\"680\" title=\"tsconfig.json\" class=\"gt n o gs ac\" scrolling=\"auto\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 680px; height: 236.984px; position: absolute;\"></iframe></div></div></figure><p id=\"8968\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">When&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">target</code>&nbsp;is set to&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">es2015</code>, we generate and label two bundles.</p><p id=\"bf12\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">At runtime, the browser uses attributes on the script tag to load the right bundle.</p><p id=\"f0e7\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">&lt;script type=\"module\" src=\"…\"&gt;</code>&nbsp;// Modern JS</p><p id=\"16fa\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">&lt;script nomodule src=\"…\"&gt;</code>&nbsp;// Legacy JS</p><p id=\"13a3\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">On&nbsp;<a href=\"https://angular.io/\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">angular.io</a>&nbsp;we saved over 40kB of initial bundle size for modern browsers. From the community we’ve heard that applications generally save 7–20% of their bundle size, depending on the amount of modern JavaScript features they take advantage of.</p><figure class=\"ls lt lu lv lw fg y z paragraph-image\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 56px auto 0px; clear: both; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"lx ly eu lz ac\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; width: 680px; position: relative; transition: transform 300ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0.2, 1) 0s; cursor: zoom-in; z-index: auto;\"><div class=\"y z nn\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 928px;\"><div class=\"md l eu me\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; margin: auto; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\"><div class=\"no l\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding-bottom: 393.484px;\"><div class=\"dn ma gt n o gs ac cp mb mc\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 680px; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0; height: 393.484px; position: absolute; transition: opacity 100ms ease 400ms; will-change: transform; transform: translateZ(0px);\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"gt n o gs ac mg mh ob oc\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/30/0*14n4CbwyOkp0uaO6?q=20\" width=\"928\" height=\"537\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 680px; height: 393.484px; position: absolute; filter: blur(20px); transform: scale(1.1); visibility: hidden; transition: visibility 0ms ease 400ms;\"></div><img alt=\"\" class=\"nu nv gt n o gs ac gq\" width=\"928\" height=\"537\" role=\"presentation\" src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/928/0*14n4CbwyOkp0uaO6\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 680px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 393.484px; position: absolute; opacity: 1; transition: opacity 400ms ease 0ms;\"></div></div></div></div><figcaption class=\"cf ej mj mk hv dl y z ml mm aw ei\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.54); max-width: 728px; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.4; margin-top: 10px;\">The bundle size on angular.io shrunk by about 41Kb</figcaption></figure><p id=\"1a17\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Learn more about&nbsp;<a href=\"https://v8.angular.io/guide/deployment#differential-loading\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">differential loading</a>.</p><h1 id=\"b722\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\"><span class=\"bj\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Route Configurations use Dynamic Imports</span></h1><p id=\"e133\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">We highly recommend you lazily load parts of your application using the router. This is accomplished by using the&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">loadChildren</code>&nbsp;key in your route configuration.</p><p id=\"2abc\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Previously this looked like:</p><p id=\"e60c\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">{path: \'/admin\', loadChildren: \'./admin/admin.module#AdminModule\'}</code></p><p id=\"a747\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">This syntax was custom to Angular and built into our toolchain. With version 8 we’re migrating to the industry standard&nbsp;<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/import\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">dynamic imports</a>.</p><p id=\"ec6f\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Now this will look like:</p><p id=\"6d43\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">{path: `/admin`, loadChildren: () =&gt; import(`./admin/admin.module`).then(m =&gt; m.AdminModule)}</code></p><p id=\"c99e\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">This will improve the support from editors like&nbsp;<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">VSCode</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">WebStorm</a>&nbsp;who will now be able to understand and validate these imports for you.</p><p id=\"838d\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">If you use&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng update</code>, we’ll update your code automatically to use the new best practice.</p><h1 id=\"70a1\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\"><span class=\"bj\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Builder APIs in the CLI</span></h1><p id=\"4d9b\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">In the same way that Schematics allow you to tap into&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng new</code>&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng generate</code>&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng add</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng update</code>, we’ve released new Builder APIs that allow you to tap into&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng build</code>&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng test</code>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng run</code>&nbsp;to perform processes like build and deployment.</p><p id=\"ef34\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Check out&nbsp;<a class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://blog.angular.io/introducing-cli-builders-d012d4489f1b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">our blog post on these new APIs</a>.</p><p id=\"aaf7\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Or read&nbsp;<a href=\"https://v8.angular.io/guide/cli-builder\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">the API documentation</a>.</p><p id=\"1c90\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">We’ve also been working with cloud providers to begin taking advantage of these APIs. Today you can try the latest version of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angularfire2\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">AngularFire</a>, which adds a&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">deploy</code>&nbsp;command, making build &amp; deploy to Firebase easier than ever:</p><pre class=\"ls lt lu lv lw ht ft cw\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-bottom: 0px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 20px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);\"><span id=\"2315\" class=\"np mo ef ax nl b ej nq nr l ns\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: block; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace; line-height: 1.18; margin-top: -0.09em; margin-bottom: -0.09em; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ng add @angular/fire<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">ng run my-app:deploy</span></pre><p id=\"b2b3\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Once installed, this deployment command will both build and deploy your application in the way recommended by AngularFire.</p><h1 id=\"bad5\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\"><span class=\"bj\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Workspace APIs in the CLI</span></h1><p id=\"8d7a\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Previously developers using&nbsp;<a href=\"https://angular.io/guide/schematics\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Schematics</a>&nbsp;had to manually open and modify their&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">angular.json</code>&nbsp;to make changes to the workspace configuration. With 8.0, we’re introducing a new API to make it easier to read and modify this file.</p><p id=\"6dde\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Read more about the available&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cli/blob/master/packages/angular_devkit/core/README.md#workspaces\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Workspace APIs</a>.</p><h1 id=\"ac54\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\">Web Worker Support</h1><p id=\"4378\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Using_web_workers\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Web workers</a>&nbsp;are a great way to speed up your application if you do any sort of cpu-intensive processing. Web workers allow you to offload work to a background thread, such as image or video manipulation. We use web workers on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://angular.io/\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">angular.io</a>&nbsp;for in-app search indexing.</p><p id=\"cb3a\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">You can now generate new web workers from the CLI. To add a worker to your project, you can run:</p><p id=\"9a2f\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ng generate webWorker my-worker</code></p><p id=\"65f5\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Once you have a web worker, you can use it normally in your application, and the CLI will be able to bundle and code split it correctly:</p><p id=\"4e01\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">const worker = new Worker(`./my-worker.worker`, { type: `module` });</code></p><p id=\"fd01\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Read more about&nbsp;<a href=\"https://v8.angular.io/guide/web-worker\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">web workers in the Angular CLI</a>.</p><h1 id=\"802d\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\"><span class=\"bj\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">AngularJS Migration Improvements</span></h1><p id=\"6403\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">If you use the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.angularjs.org/api/ng/service/$location\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">$location service</a>&nbsp;in an AngularJS application, Angular now provides a&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">LocationUpgradeModule</code>&nbsp;that enables a unified location service that shifts responsibilities from the AngularJS&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">$location</code>&nbsp;service to the Angular&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">Location</code>&nbsp;Service. This should improve the lives of applications using&nbsp;<code class=\"me nj nk nl b\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 2px 4px; font-size: 15.75px; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, Courier, monospace;\">ngUpgrade</code>&nbsp;who need routing in both the AngularJS and Angular part of their application.</p><p id=\"6d31\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Read more about the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://v8.angular.io/guide/upgrade#using-the-unified-angular-location-service\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Unified Angular Location Service</a>.</p><p id=\"eeac\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">We’ve also documented best practices around lazy loading parts of your AngularJS application from Angular, making it easier to migrate the most commonly used features first, and only loading AngularJS for a subset of your application.</p><p id=\"6f44\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">Read more about&nbsp;<a href=\"https://v8.angular.io/guide/upgrade#create-a-service-to-lazy-load-angularjs\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Lazy Loading AngularJS</a>.</p><h1 id=\"aa0d\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\"><span class=\"bj\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">New Deprecation Guide</span></h1><p id=\"fd47\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">We are committed to maintaining Semantic Versioning and a high degree of stability even across major versions. For our public API, we are committed to supporting features for N+2 releases. This means that a feature that is deprecated in 8.1 will keep working in the following two major releases (9 and 10). For example, we are deprecating platform-webworker in version 8.</p><p id=\"64ca\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg lh li lj lk ll lm ln lo lp lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 2em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">We are making it easier to find deprecations and removals in Angular. For a comprehensive list of all deprecations, see the new&nbsp;<a href=\"https://v8.angular.io/guide/deprecations\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Deprecation Guide</a>.</p><h1 id=\"a14f\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\"><span class=\"bj\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Ivy &amp; Bazel</span></h1><p id=\"b3e2\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px;\">We know there’s lots of excitement for our forthcoming opt-in previews. We’ll be providing individual updates on these next week on this blog, so stay tuned!</p><h1 id=\"87d6\" class=\"mn mo ef ax aw ed mp mq mr ms mt mu mv mw mx my mz\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 1.95em 0px -0.28em; font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans&quot;, Geneva, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.12; letter-spacing: -0.022em; font-size: 34px;\">Contributors and Collaborators</h1><p><figure class=\"ls lt lu lv lw fg\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 56px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: medium-content-sans-serif-font, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"md l eu\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; margin: auto;\"></div></figure></p><p id=\"1784\" class=\"ld le ef ax lf b lg na li nb lk nc lm nd lo ne lq\" data-selectable-paragraph=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0.86em 0px -0.46em; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84); line-height: 1.58; letter-spacing: -0.004em; font-family: medium-content-serif-font, Georgia, Cambria, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; font-size: 21px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">A special thanks to<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ManfredSteyer\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Manfred Steyer</a><span>&nbsp;</span>for contributing to Differential Loading,<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/phenomnominal\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Craig Spence</a><span>&nbsp;</span>to Dynamic Import support,<span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://twitter.com/_developit\" class=\"dx cb nf ng nh ni\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg preserveAspectRatio=\\&quot;none\\&quot; viewBox=\\&quot;0 0 1 1\\&quot; xmlns=\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\&quot;><line x1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; y1=\\&quot;0\\&quot; x2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; y2=\\&quot;1\\&quot; stroke=\\&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.84)\\&quot; /></svg>&quot;); background-size: 1px 1px; background-position: 0px calc(1em + 1px);\">Jason Miller</a><span>&nbsp;</span>to Web Worker bundling support. This release was brought to you by 286 contributors:</p>', 'version-8-of-angular-smaller-bundles-cli-apis-and-alignment-with-the-ecosystem', 'uploads/posts/1567269043499786.png', 1, '2019-08-31 10:30:43', '2019-08-31 10:30:43', NULL, 1);
