) !important;\"><code class=\"shell-session hljs sql\" style=\"margin: 0px 3px 0px 1px; list-style: none; border: 0px rgb(21, 195, 154); outline: none; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, MonacoRegular, monospace; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; display: block; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-x: auto; padding: 20px !important;\">pip <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(167, 29, 93);\">install</span> Django</code></pre><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(44, 47, 52); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">This will install the latest version of Django in our virtual Environment. To know more about Django installation read:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://djangocentral.com/how-to-install-django/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(21, 195, 154); transition: all 0.15s ease 0s;\">How To Install Django</a></p><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(44, 47, 52); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; font-weight: 600;\">Note –&nbsp;</span>You must install a version of Django greater than 2.0</p><h2 style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 600; font-size: 27px; color: rgb(44, 47, 52); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">Setting Up The Project</h2><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(44, 47, 52); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">In your workspace create a directory called&nbsp;<code style=\"padding: 0.125em 0.25em; margin: 0px 3px 0px 1px; list-style: none; border: 0px rgb(21, 195, 154); outline: none; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, MonacoRegular, monospace; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6; background-color: rgb(245, 247, 248); color: rgb(255, 56, 96); border-radius: 4px;\">mysite</code>&nbsp;and navigate into it.</p><div class=\"stream-item stream-item-in-post stream-item-inline-post aligncenter\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 6px auto; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; clear: both; color: rgb(44, 47, 52); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"></div><pre style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; list-style: none; border: none; outline: none; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, MonacoRegular, monospace; font-size: 17px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(63, 59, 54); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-size: initial; direction: ltr; tab-size: 2; border-radius: 2px; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249) !important;\"><code class=\"language-python hljs\" style=\"margin: 0px 3px 0px 1px; list-style: none; border: 0px rgb(21, 195, 154); outline: none; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, MonacoRegular, monospace; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; display: block; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-x: auto; padding: 20px !important;\">cd Desktop\r\nmkdir mysite\r\ncd mysite</code></pre><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(44, 47, 52); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">Now run the following command in your shell to create a Django project.</p><pre style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; list-style: none; border: none; outline: none; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, MonacoRegular, monospace; font-size: 17px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(63, 59, 54); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-size: initial; direction: ltr; tab-size: 2; border-radius: 2px; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249) !important;\"><code class=\"language-python hljs\" style=\"margin: 0px 3px 0px 1px; list-style: none; border: 0px rgb(21, 195, 154); outline: none; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, MonacoRegular, monospace; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; display: block; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-x: auto; padding: 20px !important;\">django-admin startproject mysite</code></pre><p style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(44, 47, 52); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Oxygen-Sans, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">This will generate a project structure with several directories and python scripts.</p><pre style=\"padding: 0px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; list-style: none; border: none; outline: none; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, MonacoRegular, monospace; font-size: 17px; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(63, 59, 54); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-size: initial; direction: ltr; tab-size: 2; border-radius: 2px; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249) !important;\"><code class=\"language-python hljs\" style=\"margin: 0px 3px 0px 1px; list-style: none; border: 0px rgb(21, 195, 154); outline: none; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, MonacoRegular, monospace; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; display: block; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-x: auto; padding: 20px !important;\">├── mysite\r\n│   ├── __init__<span class=\"hljs-selector-class\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: no